-- CHOSON
-- ============================================================================
UPDATE countries SET country_brief = $$
Choson is the world's most dangerous minor power — a nuclear-armed totalitarian state with 0.3 coins GDP, the smallest economy in the simulation by an order of magnitude, and a talent for manufacturing crises at the worst possible moment for everyone else. Supreme Leader Pyro, in his early forties, has cemented power after a decade of purges and nuclear tests. In March 2026, he vowed to "irreversibly cement" Choson's nuclear status, ordering accelerated missile production and expanded ICBM complexes. The nuclear arsenal is estimated at 40-60 warheads with an expanding delivery capability — land-based ICBMs that can theoretically reach Columbia's continental territory, submarine-launched missiles (development accelerated by Sarmatian technology transfers), and tactical nuclear weapons for battlefield use.

